sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.ia64

Class IA64ThreadContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.ia64.IA64ThreadContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ThreadContext
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinuxIA64ThreadContext

    public abstract class IA64ThreadContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements ThreadContext
    Specifies the thread context on ia64 platform; only a sub-portion of the context is guaranteed to be present on all operating systems.
